      <title>可可成本拖累巧克力销售，百乐嘉利宝股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/barry-callebaut-slumps-as-cocoa-prices-pressure-chocolate-demand</link>
